Posts.Content: Hi Mark, have you seen Doc yet?. I'm sure its not about Prostate cancer,as you are young there not be any chance for PC. This may be some other inflammation which occurs in teenage time(hormonal change). Go through National Cancer Institute Prostate Cancer Symptoms Guide .Most often prostate cancer happens to come after 50+ old men & is least probable to find it in early stage.
